U7 nng7-e5 peng-a2, long2 si7 1984 ni5 chhut-si3--e5, chit8-e5 kok-tiong chhut-giap8 to7 leh kang-te7 cho3 khang-khoe3, ho7-cho3 “Hiok--a2”, si7 poaN-soa2 loh8-lai5 Hong-goan5 e5 Tayal; leng7-goa7 chit8-e5 kok-tiong thak8 bo5 thau3, ma7 u7 cho3 chit8-cham7-a2 khang-khoe3, lang5 long2 kio3 i “Tang2--e5”. Hiok--a2 bou2 chhoa7--a, kiann2 ma7 seN--a, sui-bong2 ni5-hoe3 iau2 sng3 chio2, m7-koh e7-sai2 kong2 i2-keng u7 tam7-poh8-a2 sia7-hoe7 keng-giam7--a.
U7 chit8-pai2, Hiok--a2 hioh gou7-kang ka2, chiau3-li2 kong2, pai3-si3 hit-jit8 ai3 siu-ka2 tng2--lai5, tui7--nih kui-teng7 chhit-tiam2 chin3-cheng5 ai3 oan5-seng5 siu-ka2 e5 teng5-su5. Kau3 chap8-tiam2 beh khun3--a, soah iau2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 lang5, kun-koaN ham7 su7-koaN lau7--e5 hoan5-lo2 i e7 chhut i3-goa7, ma7 siuN7 bo5 i u7 jin7-ho5 to5-peng e5 tong7-ki: kam2-cheng5 un2-teng7, cho3-peng-a2-lang5 goeh8-kip iu2-han7, ma7 bo5 thiaN-koe3 i teh ai, kun-tiong e5 choan-giap8 ki-sut8 sui-bong2 oh-laiu2 u7 khah ban7, chong2--si7 “giam7-siu” ma7 long2 u7 koe3.
Chit8-kang, nng7-kang, saN-kang, kau3 te7-gou7-kang, tui7-a2 be7 kham-tit tan2--a, beh ka7 “li7-iaN5 thong-po3” hoat--chhut-khi3, ti7 chit-e5 si5-chun7, koh it-tit8 ham7 in tau e5 lang5 lian5-lok8, ma7 long2 iau2 bo5 i e5 siau-sit, ui5-it khak-teng7--e5 si7 i chau2 be7 ku2, sin-khu tann-a2 saN-chheng-khou. Te7-gou7-kang e5 si5, in tau e5 lang5 chong2-sng3 chiap-tioh8 i kha3--tng2-khi3 e5 tian7-oe7, sui5 to7 ka7 tui7--nih kong2, e7 chhin-sin ka7 i chai3-lai5 Cho2-iaN5. Tan2 i tng2--lai5, chiah thiaN in thin5-siong7 e5 su7-koaN lau7--e5 kong2, kai siu-ka2 hit-kang, i kau3 Cho2-iaN5 e5 si5 to7 chhian5 chit8-tiam2-cheng ku2--a, m7-kaN2 kha3 tian7-oe7 tng2 tui7--nih, ma7 m7-kaN2 kha3 tian7-oe7 tng2 chhu3--nih, choann-a2 ti7『網咖』chiu2 gou7-kang, bo5-chiN5--a chiah ham7 chhu3--nih lian5-lok8.
To5-peng ti7 kun-tiong tiann7 thiaN-kong2, m7-koh na7 m7-si7 toa3 be7 tiau5, to7-si7 kam2-cheng5 in-sou3, iau2 m7-bat u7 chhiuN7 i an2-ne: si5-kan be7-hu3--a, to7 kui-khi3 mai3 tng2--khi3. Chit chan5 tai7-chi3 hian2-si7, i bo5 chhu2-li2 tai7-chi3 e5 leng5-lek8, tu2-tioh8 tai7-chi3 to7 siuN7 beh siam2, an2-ne beh an2-choann2 chhiann5 i e5 gin2-a2? Khah hou7 lang5 hoan5-lo2--e5 si7, chit-ma2 e5 siau3-lian5-lang5 kam2 long2 an2-ne? Mai3 kong2 beh sio-chian3 iah beh kian3-kok, lian5 cho3-lang5 e5 lau7-pe7, chhu2-li2 ka-ti7 e5 su7-hang7 khiong2-kiaN to u7 bun7-te5--a, i koh si7 u7 tam7-poh8-a2 sia7-hoe7 keng-giam7--e5. Na7 tann-a2 i chit8-e5 an2-ne, hoan7-se3 si7 goa2 siuN7 siunn che7. M7-koh goan2 tui7--nih leng7-goa7 chit8-e5 soah koh ju2 ham3-kou2.
Tang2--e5 pang3-ka2 hit-kang, ui3 Cho2-iaN5 che7 ba2-suh kau3 Ko-hiong5 hoe2-chhia-thau5, kau3 hia chiah hoat-hian7 chiN5-te7-a2 phang2--khi3, m7-kaN2 kha3 tian7-oe7 tng2-khi3 tui7--nih, ma7 m7-kaN2 kap chhu3--nih lian5-lok8, to7 iong7 kiaN5--e5, kiaN5 nng7-kang chiah tng2 kau3 Cho2-iaN5 (tiong-ng koh kiaN5 bo5--khi3). Che sit8-chai7 hou7 lang5 siuN7 bo5, i soah m7-chai chhia-thau5 long2 u7 kun-jin5 hok8-bu7-cham7? I kam2 m7-chai e7-sai2 chhoe7 keng2-chhat?
ChhiuN7 chit-khoan2 ki5-ki5-khoai3-khoai3 e5 tai7-chi3, ti7 goan2 tui7--nih e7-sai2 kong2 chin su3-siong5, khah hoan5-lo2 --e5 si7, che to7-si7 chin2 siau3-lian5-ke e5 sou3-chit, pau-khoah chin3-cheng5 thiaN-tioh8『草莓世代』e5 chiong2-chiong2 ham3-kou2, lan2 kam2 be7 hoan5-lo2? Kau3 si5-chun7, in ai3 lai5 keng chit-e5 kok-ka neh?
Siong5-se3 ka7 siuN7, che si7 an2-choann2 cho7-chiann5--e5?
(TGB Thong-sin3 te7 66 ki5, 2005 ni5 3 goeh8)
